    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>eabus</ex></expan> Nymphis <lb n="2"/>vicani Al<lb break="no" n="3"/>tiaienses aram <expan><abbr>posuer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>cura Octoni <lb n="5"/>Terti et Castoni <lb n="6"/>Cassi X <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Dec</abbr><ex>embres</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Maximo et Aeliano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Text 1 befindet sich auf der corona; Text 3 auf der crepido. Z. 1: IN-Ligatur; Z. 5: AM-, VE-Ligaturen; Z. 6: OC miteinander verschränkt; Z. 7: NI-Ligatur; Z. 9: ET-Ligatur. Einige Buchstaben kleiner geschrieben.</p>
            </div>
